data.description:
Experience luxury living in this exquisite home located in the popular Splawn Ranch neighborhood of Killeen. As you step inside, the spacious living room greets you with elegant tray ceilings and an abundance of natural light. The French doors lead you to a beautifully improved patio area, complete with a charming gazebo and practical storage shed.

The heart of this home is the expansive primary bedroom, featuring a luxurious tray ceiling. The ensuite is a haven of relaxation with its double vanity, indulgent jetted tub, walk-in shower, and his and hers closets.

Culinary enthusiasts will adore the well-appointed kitchen, boasting stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, and a delightful eat-in area. For your professional needs, the home includes a tranquil office study area for work or study. Adding to the home’s practicality is the convenient indoor laundry.

Situated in a prime location, this property offers easy access to shopping, dining, and more, ensuring that convenience is always at your fingertips. This home is a perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and practicality. Don’t miss the opportunity to embrace the exceptional lifestyle it offers – schedule a showing today!
